Package: ROpenCVLite
Type: Package
Title: Install OpenCV Within R
Version: 0.1.31
Author: Simon Garnier
Maintainer: Simon Garnier <garnier@njit.edu>
Description: This is a utility package that installs OpenCV within R for use by
    other packages. This Lite version does not contain any of the contributed
    modules of OpenCV.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
